Congress is about to pass a budget. I call it a &ldquo;Paul Ryan Special.&rdquo; This budget lets the government spend money for four months. It expires in September.
The budget is horrible. Republicans are spinning a few &ldquo;wins&rdquo; in the budget, but that&rsquo;s a terrible argument. It&rsquo;s like telling a terminal cancer patient, &ldquo;but your blood pressure&rsquo;s pretty good.&rdquo;
Here&rsquo;s the thing: you cannot control Congress. You can only control what you focus on and what you do next.
